{
  "stem": "13258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's-- so I-- we have two places already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have Oswiemcim, Auschwitz, and we have Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's not the rest-- it's not all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We come to others which have become notorious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the train-- but by that time, we still are on passenger trains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had only one ticket to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And since then, we hadn't bought any tickets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And nobody bothered to ask us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We hadn't any food with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the train wasn't really going very fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We-- sometimes we were standing for two hours under a semaphore, under a signal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then some farmers would come and sell something to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In one place, we got some rutabagas, I think, from the field.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we're eating raw rutabagas or so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It didn't matter-- whatever there was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then, we came to a place called Debica, D-E with a little tail B-I-C-A.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There, we got off the train because not far from there was a Jewish farm in which I had spent vacation once.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said, that would be a good place to be because probably the farm they wouldn't bomb.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it would be nice to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But first, we went into the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And as we walked out of the station, there were two big craters, huge, from bombs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the one had been a hotel once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there was nothing left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we went in the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I see, like today, there is a dairy store.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there's a sign in the window, 'We're back soon.' And inside, there is such a massive block of butter with a knife in it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there's nobody there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But the door is closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father went-- and we went in the center.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
